# ===== NOTES =====
# This .gitignore prevents committing:
# 1. Credential files (gcloud-user-credentials.json, n8n-*-key.json, manifest.json)
# 2. Large data files (CSV, Excel, database files)
# 3. Generated outputs and temporary files
# 4. System/IDE files
# 5. Logs and cache files
#
# But DOES commit:
# - All source code (Python, SQL, JavaScript, etc.)
# - Documentation files (Markdown)
# - Configuration templates (not actual credentials)
# - Model metadata JSON files (not credentials)
